  "title": "Finance Executive/ Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Position Type: </strong>1-Year Contract<br /><br /><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Coordinate end-to-end bank direct debit conversion activities</p></li><li><p>Liaise with Accounts Receivable teams and banks</p></li><li><p>Work with banking partners to manage migration requirements and timelines</p></li><li><p>Review bank documentation and facilitate completion of authorized signatories</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with Taidii system vendors and banks to set up eGIRO arrangements in the ABS portal</p></li><li><p>Ensure customer mandates and bank requirements are accurately captured and validated</p></li><li><p>Monitor conversion progress, follow up on outstanding items, and resolve issues</p></li><li><p>Maintain proper and accurate documentation</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Minimum of 2 years’ relevant working experience</p></li><li><p>Diploma in Accounting<br /></p></li></ul><p><em></em></p>",
