    "description": "<p><strong>Global EduHub&nbsp;</strong>is a professional preschool management solutions provider, currently managing over 36 premium schools in Singapore. We manage childcare brands like Mulberry Learning Centre, Alpabet Playhouse, Little Green House and School House Bythe garden . Mainly cater to different target markets, offering a complete menu of educational services ranging from infant care, childcare, student care, playgroup, kindergarten, tuition and enrichment programme.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>With our full suite of management solutions, We strengthen the competency of preschools in delivering quality education consistently, anywhere in the world. We collaborate closely with our partners to create ideal conditions, from the curricula to the physical environment, to foster a child's holistic development.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Our purpose is not just to prepare each child for formal education, but for a lifetime ahead.</p>",
